U.S.: Repeating is the mother of wisdom
It is funny that Barack Obama, the president with the reputation of the smartest man, as a diligent student repeats in the Afghan question the strategy of his predecessor, whom he himself took for the dumbest.
When he finally revealed his Afghan approach, waited anxiously, it was shown that it was a copy of the script used for Iraq by Bush, created three years ago.
